title: 02/25/21 DPS Hour 3 Tim Legler

description:
Tim Legler tells Dan that the Lakers will be fine as long as Anthony Davis is healthy and is playing at a high level. Tim says that the Jazz may have a lot to say about that, but the Lakers have nothing to worry about.
